  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Parody World: Monster Party is the Japanese release of Monster Party, and was originally intended to be much darker and more morbid than the relatively light-hearted version that was ultimately released to American gamers. No version of the game was ever released in Japan. The unreleased Japanese Famicom version was leaked online in August 13th, 2014.",
